Examples: "customers/my_customer/apps/chrome/gmbmikajjgmnabiglmofipeabaddhgne@2.1.2" for the Save to Google Drive Chrome extension version 2.1.2, "customers/my_customer/apps/android/com.google.android.apps.docs" for the Google Drive Android app's latest version.
